{
  "completion_percentage": 50
}

### Update Progress (100% - Completed)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/progress/resource/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completion_percentage": 100
}

### Get My Progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

